subject: Coaches and Managers
Baseball
lead_paragraph: The contracts of the Colorado Rockies’ hitting instructor, Carney Lansford, and their third-base coach, Rich Dauer, were not renewed in the wake of Manager Jim Tracy’s unexpected resignation.
